pplications was done by Goldman Design, while Integrum completed implementation.<\/p>\n<p>The iPhone and Android applications are available for download from the <a href=\"http:\/\/itunes.apple.com\/app\/superpages\/id304932294?mt=8\" target=\"_blank\">AppStore<\/a> and <a href=\"http:\/\/www.superpages.com\/mobile\/android\" target=\"_blank\">Android Market<\/a>.<\/p>\n","protected":false},"excerpt":{"rendered":"<p>Goldman Design, on behalf of\u00a0Superpages,\u00a0came to us looking for a complete interface redesign of their iPhone and Android applications. Superpages, which provides information on local &hellip;<\/p>\n","protected":false},"author":5,"featured_media":0,"comment_status":"open","ping_status":"open","sticky":false,"template":"","format":"standard","meta":[],"categories":[5],"tags":[],"_links":{"self":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5071"}],"collection":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts"}],"about":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/types\/post"}],"author":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/users\/5"}],"replies":[{"embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/comments?post=5071"}],"version-history":[{"count":0,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/posts\/5071\/revisions"}],"wp:attachment":[{"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/media?parent=5071"}],"wp:term":[{"taxonomy":"category","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/categories?post=5071"},{"taxonomy":"post_tag","embeddable":true,"href":"http:\/\/integrumtech.com\/wp-json\/wp\/v2\/tags?post=5071"}],"curies":[{"name":"wp","href":"https:\/\/api.w.org\/{rel}","templated":true}]}}